ackEvent\"><code>AnimationPlaybackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/getAnimations\"><code>Document.getAnimations()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/timeline\"><code>Document.timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentTimeline\"><code>DocumentTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Element/animate\"><code>Element.animate()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>La propiedad de solo-lectura de <code>Animation.finished</code> de la <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Web Animations API (en-US)</a> devuelve un <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> que se resuelve una vez que la animación a terminado de reproducirse.</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Nota:</strong> Una vez que la reproducción de la animación abandona el estado <code>finished</code> (es decir, la reproducción se está ejecutando otra vez), Un nuevo <code>Promise</code> es creado para esta propiedad. El nuevo <code>Promise</code> será resuelto cuando se haya completado la actual secuencia de la animación.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxis","title":"Sintaxis","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> animationsPromise <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Animation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>finished<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor","title":"Valor","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Un objeto <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> que se resuelve cuando haya finalizado la reproducción de la animación.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplos","title":"Ejemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>El siguiente código espera a que todas las animaciones que se ejecutan en el elemento <code>elem</code> hayan terminado, después elimina el elemento del arbol del DOM:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>Promise<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">all</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  elem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getAnimations</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">map</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> animation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>finished\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> elem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">remove</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Especificaciones","id":"especificaciones","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/#dom-animation-finished","title":"Web Animations"}],"query":"api.Animation.finished"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad con navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_con_navegadores","isH3":false,"query":"api.Animation.finished","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_también","title":"Ver también","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Web Animations API (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxis","id":"sintaxis"},{"text":"Ejemplos","id":"ejemplos"},{"text":"Especificaciones","id":"especificaciones"},{"text":"Compatibilidad con navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_con_navegadores"},{"text":"Ver también","id":"ver_también"}],"summary":"La propiedad de solo-lectura de Animation.finished de la Web Animations API (en-US) devuelve un Promise que se resuelve una vez que la animación a terminado de reproducirse.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Animation.finished","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Animation.finished","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/api/animation/finished","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/api/animation/finished/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API","title":"Referencia de la API Web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation","title":"Animation"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished","title":"Animation.finished"}],"pageTitle":"Animation.finished - Referencia de la API Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}